; lost this tx (can't get it in a CSV from broker_a)
; Add EUR to USDC conversion transaction
; The 10 EUR deposit was converted to USDC on broker_a (originally USDT, later
; converted to USDC due to EU regulations but going straight to USDC for
; simplicity)
; Trade spent 9.50 USDC, remaining balance is 0.50 USDC
; Total USDC received 9.50 + 0.50 = 10.00 USDC
; We use @@ to specify total EUR cost and let hledger calculate the unit rate
2024-04-03 EUR to USDC conversion on broker_a
    assets:broker-a:USDC      10.000000 USDC @@ 10.00 EUR
    assets:broker-a:especes  -10.00 EUR
